    character: "Pan Yueting",
    line: " Were you busy with Mrs. Li?"
  }, {
    character: "Li Shiqing ",
    line: " No, no. You’d better go back in to your game of mahjong."
  }, {
    character: "Li Shiqing ",
    line: " Is there any news from the newspaper office about any special change in the situation."
  }, {
    character: "Pan Yueting",
    line: " It would be no concern of yours if there were; have you bought the government bonds I told you to buy?"
  }, {
    character: "Li Shiqing ",
    line: " Yes, two million altogether, this month’s issue."
  }, {
    character: "Pan Yueting",
    line: " What sort of price did you get them for?"
  }, {
