    line: " Seven seventy-five."
  }, {
    character: "Pan Yueting",
    line: " And what happened after you’d bought?"
  }, {
    character: "Li Shiqing ",
    line: " I’m afraid it’s not a very favorable reaction. What with rumors flying and money tight and share-prices dropping all the time, and holders of government bonds offloading them; but you, sir, have to go and—"
  }, {
    character: "Pan Yueting",
    line: " I have to go and buy them up."
  }, {
