    character: "Pan Yueting",
    line: " You don’t imagine it’d be in the hope of a fall!"
  }, {
    character: "Li Shiqing ",
    line: " Mr. Pan, it’s not very risky to stock up with bonds in the ordinary way: at a pinch you can always cash them and buy them back later. But now it’s a special "
  }, {
    character: "Li Shiqing ",
    line: "situation, with prices going down and down all the time. If they should settle there’s always hope that they’ll come up again and then you’ll make a packet. But that’s something we’ve no control over."
  }, {
