  }, {
    character: "Li Shiqing ",
    line: " Of course, Mr. Pan. But I was only mentioning it to remind you."
  }, {
    character: "Pan Yueting",
    line: " The bank’s affairs are not open to discussion. Also, I don’t need your reminding. "
