    line: " Yes. I mentioned the matter of the new building that the bank’s putting up."
  }, {
    character: "Li Shiqing ",
    line: "He said he didn’t see how the bank could afford it just now. And then he went on to talk about the difficult state of the market and the way land prices are falling. "
  }, {
