    line: "And he said that as the building’s only been started, it would be advisable to stop work on it at once."
  }, {
    character: "Pan Yueting",
    line: " Haven’t you told him that the contract has been signed and that the earnest-money paid for the building?"
  }, {
    character: "Li Shiqing ",
    line: " Of course, I told him the job had been taken by a foreign contractor, so there was no question of asking for our money bank, which meant that it would be just impossible for the moment to free Mr. Jin’s deposit with us, so could he give us a couple of day’s grace."
  }, {
    character: "Pan Yueting",
    line: " What did he say to that?"
  }, {
